'''Puerto Rico''' is a [[Nations|country]] that was on BitLife in June 2019. Its default cities are the capital, San Juan, along with Ponce.

On June 9, 2019 on [[IOS version|iOS]]; new countries were added. Along with Puerto Rico; there was also [[Afghanistan]], [[Belgium]], [[Djibouti]], [[Dominican Republic]], [[Iraq]], [[Poland]], [[Switzerland]], [[Taiwan]], [[Thailand]], [[United Arab Emirates]], and [[Uruguay]]. It was added to Android September 21, 2019. Although Puerto Rico is a territory of the United States, it is treated as a country. And unlike its real life counterpart where emigrating from Puerto Rico to the United States is straightforward, the BitLife version may accept emigrants at a fee (or may not accept if they either have a criminal record or simply refuse entry).

